{"tid":1857284,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[HK-NOSTALE] Gamecyber 新夢之歷險 [02] 森林之夢","createTime":"2020-02-02T06:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T19:37:13.000Z","uid":218935,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7f08c7c72175320630fd1d3b0bb3a89c7e061e","tid":1857284,"uid":218935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:20:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">［HK-Nostale] Gamecyber 新夢之歷險</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvzZC0B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvzZC0B.png&h=5d5b3da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣告：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5gMRoFViq4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5gMRoFViq4w&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9FNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=c1a88ccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5gMRoFViq4w</a><br />\n<br />\n官方網站：<br />\n<a href=\"http://nos.gamecyber.net/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnos.gamecyber.net%2Findex.html&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9FNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=9f771b58\" target=\"_blank\">http://nos.gamecyber.net/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n簡介：<br />\n<br />\n由2007年開始於香港營運的MMORPG<br />\n<br />\n眾多玩家的童年回憶<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">於2020年1月14日追加新服：森林之夢</span><br />\n<br />\n更新7章改版<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">並正式更名為 新夢之歷險</span><br />\n<br />\n有關舊有Server現況：<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">星河之夢 / 大地之夢 (已移除)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">天空之夢(健在 , 多人掛機)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">海洋之夢/冒險之夢(已無活人)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">新Server - 森林之夢現況</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3個分流 多活人</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXXTHAq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXXTHAq.png&h=f32e4e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHccX9x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHccX9x.png&h=65ffec0d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J85NMYL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ85NMYL.png&h=25e4708c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sSCP0mo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsSCP0mo.png&h=f93a9f1f&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">開服2星期玩家數目急速增多<br />\nServer一直持續快爆了狀態</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TOPKPbK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTOPKPbK.png&h=fa1d89a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">新手地區各處都有人做任務<br />\n每日持續有水團/修團/黑團等初級遠征團<br />\n物價不會太高 (1防=6萬) (1女神=1.5萬)<br />\n即使小量Game錢都十分有價值<br />\n可以自給自足 賺錢生活所需!</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n家族：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">連登家族 - NaturalForce</span><br />\n<br />\n有興趣入族巴打於Game內<br />\n<br />\n聯絡：超級攻擊豌豆 <br />\n<br />\n或任何家管以上人士<br />\n<br />\n［由於初期人數有限 如位置不夠］<br />\n<br />\n有興趣巴打可自薦開設2號族<br />\n<br />\nP.S 現有連登家族只有 NaturalForce ,<br />\n早前帖文提及的其他家族與連登並無關係 , 請注意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">現時活動(進行中）：</span><br />\n2020冒險家特訓團 （僅限 森林之夢）<br />\n<a href=\"http://nos.gamecyber.net/news/20200123_e.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnos.gamecyber.net%2Fnews%2F20200123_e.htm&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9FNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=9d044f65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nos.gamecyber.net/news/20200123_e.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有任何疑問 /意見可於本Post提問 回覆 及 討論<br />\n<br />\n歡迎推Post 令更多人可認識並暢遊Nostale<br />\n<br />\n謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">此為台港澳版夢之歷險討論帖 , 其他國家版本請自行開帖討論多謝合作!</span>"},{"pid":"f7460d99d2b50c70bbd8df4f3ae5d87979490201","tid":1857284,"uid":218935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"舊POST :<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1826365/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1826365/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8b682ddfa9e2889f3fe8e537051661eaaad801c8","tid":1857284,"uid":62068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:59:34.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"57c6fc6d9fa1a3fa00f8851782460784d1660ffb","tid":1857284,"uid":218935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:01:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">資料有誤 ( 重開 post 勿推勿回</span></span>"},{"pid":"028457d615521585881f03b603e0533fb276d02f","tid":1857284,"uid":51857,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3eFmRJC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3eFmRJC.jpg&h=84846f37&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n美服玩家LM"},{"pid":"6c129a632beb355cb0b636b71b2f42e7ab34d58b","tid":1857284,"uid":135961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:27:58.000Z","msg":"有天空舊帳想玩返應該入天空定森林 天空有光弓12 同幾張+9"},{"pid":"b43e03f412acef18a5ed04e79cb81f780f4e7336","tid":1857284,"uid":69311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c129a632beb355cb0b636b71b2f42e7ab34d58b","tid":1857284,"uid":135961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:27:58.000Z","msg":"有天空舊帳想玩返應該入天空定森林 天空有光弓12 同幾張+9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T19:37:13.000Z","msg":"天空"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8b682ddfa9e2889f3fe8e537051661eaaad801c8","tid":1857284,"uid":62068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:59:34.000Z","msg":"LM"}}